    "story": {
      "title": "Our Story",
      "paragraph1": "Darasaone was founded in 2026 with a simple vision: to bridge the gap between traditional Islamic education and modern technology. We saw that many talented teachers lacked the tools to reach students beyond their local communities.",
      "paragraph2": "Today, we're building a platform that empowers teachers to create, manage, and sell their courses online, while providing students with a rich, interactive learning experience. From Quran memorization to Arabic grammar, our platform hosts courses on a wide range of Islamic subjects.",
